description: Welcome to this bright and spacious one-bedroom home at the highly sought-after FP3 building, a historic loft conversion in the vibrant Seaport District. This stunning, contemporary unit boasts large windows, soaring ceilings, and beautiful hardwood floors. The modern kitchen features sleek Arclinea cabinetry and stainless steel appliances, complemented by the convenience of in-unit laundry. Located in a converted 1890s Boston Wharf warehouse, FP3’s lobby offers a rotating art gallery, reflecting the neighborhood’s rich artistic history. Building amenities include a 24-hour concierge, professional management, and a shared rooftop deck with spectacular views. Situated in a premier location, this home provides unmatched convenience, just steps from an array of shops, restaurants, Trader Joe’s, and with easy access to South Station, public transportation, Logan Airport, and major highways. Seller welcomes offers w/ requests for buyer concessions. Plenty of rental parking nearby
